This is an **Nx + pnpm monorepo** with a mixed stack. Full entrypoint: [AGENTS.md](mdc:AGENTS.md). Architecture + data flow: [.ai/architecture.md](mdc:.ai/architecture.md).

Apps and infra:

- `apps/timemanager` — Flutter (Dart) client. Runtime: flutter (`pubspec.yaml`).
- `apps/timemanager-api` — Pylon GraphQL + Kysely + Postgres, on `:3000`. Runtime: **Deno** (`deno.json`).
- `apps/spendmanager` — Flutter spending tracker. Runtime: flutter (`pubspec.yaml`).
- `apps/spendmanager-api` — Pylon GraphQL + Kysely + Postgres (`spendmanager` DB), on `:3002`. Runtime: **Deno** (`deno.json`).
- `apps/user-manager-web` — React + Vite + SuperTokens. Runtime: node (pnpm).
- `apps/user-manager-api` — Express + SuperTokens, on `:3001`. Runtime: node (pnpm).
- `infra/timemanager-db` — Postgres `:5432` + pgAdmin `:8080` (docker-compose); hosts `timemanager` and `spendmanager` databases.
- `infra/authentik` — Authentik auth (docker-compose).
- `libs/design_system` — Shared Flutter Material 3 design system (`scope:shared`, `type:lib`).
- `libs/app_core` — Shared Flutter auth / GraphQL / prefs (`scope:shared`, `type:lib`).
- `libs/local_notifications` — Shared local OS / in-session browser notifications (`scope:shared`, `type:lib`).
- `libs/deno_api_kit` — Shared Deno Pylon/Kysely API infra (`scope:shared`, `type:lib`).
- `libs/` — reserved for additional shared packages.

Golden rules:

- Run tasks via Nx from the repo root; each app owns its runtime/package manager — never mix them.
- Node apps use **pnpm**; `timemanager-api` uses **Deno**; `timemanager` uses **Flutter**.
- Do not hand-edit generated output (`dist/`, `.nx/cache/`, Flutter `build/`, `.dart_tool/`, `node_modules/`, docker `data/`).
- Check settled choices/scope in [.ai/decisions.md](mdc:.ai/decisions.md) before structural changes.
- New local runtime/CLI → update `scripts/setup-*.sh` and [.ai/local-setup.md](mdc:.ai/local-setup.md) together.
